recipes.name: Soup
recipes.instructions:
1. Chop the vegetables 
2. Boil them in water
3. Add seasonings
4. Serve hot

recipes.name: Pasta
recipes.instructions:
1. Boil the pasta
2. Prepare the sauce
3. Mix and cook briefly
4. Serve with garnish

recipes.name: Salad
recipes.ingredients: lettuce, cucumber, tomatoes, olive oil, lemon
recipes.instructions:
1. Chop all vegetables
 2. Mix in a bowl
3. Add olive oil and lemon juice
4. Toss and serve

recipes.name: Dessert
recipes.instructions:
1. Mix ingredients
2. Bake at 350°F for 45 minutes
3. Cool and serve

recipes.name: Smoothie
recipes.instructions:
1. Combine all ingredients in a blender
2. Blend until smooth
3. Pour into a glass and enjoy

recipes.name: Grilled Chicken
recipes.ingredients: chicken breast, olive oil, garlic, rosemary
recipes.instructions:
1. Marinate chicken with olive oil, garlic, and rosemary
2. Heat the grill to medium heat
3. Cook the chicken until fully done
4. Serve with a side of vegetables

recipes.name: Pizza
recipes.ingredients: pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella, pepperoni
recipes.instructions:
1. Preheat the oven to 475°F
2. Spread tomato sauce on the dough
3. Add mozzarella and pepperoni
4. Bake for 20 minutes or until crust is golden

recipes.name: Avocado Toast
recipes.instructions:
1. Toast the bread
2. Mash avocado and spread on toast
3. Sprinkle with salt and chili flakes
4. Serve immediately

recipes.name: Omelette
recipes.instructions:
1. Beat eggs with milk
2. Pour into a hot skillet
3. Add cheese and spinach
4. Cook until set and fold in half

recipes.name: Stir Fry
recipes.ingredients: broccoli, carrots, soy sauce, sesame oil
recipes.instructions:
1. Heat sesame oil in a pan
2. Add vegetables and stir-fry
3. Add soy sauce and cook for 5 minutes
4. Serve hot over rice
